---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="Mental Wellbeing Case Study" description="Designing a culturally sensitive mental health ecosystem.">
  <article class="prose max-w-none">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <a
        href="/projects"
        class="no-underline text-zinc-400 hover:text-white text-sm font-bold flex items-center gap-2 mb-8 transition-colors"
      >
        <span class="i-carbon-arrow-left"></span> Back to Projects
      </a>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-6">
        <span
          class="bg-emerald-900/40 text-emerald-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-mono border border-emerald-800/50"
        >
          <span class="i-carbon-user-speaker mr-1 align-middle"></span> 1st Author (IEEE)
        </span>
        <span
          class="bg-purple-900/40 text-purple-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-mono border border-purple-800/50"
        >
          <span class="i-carbon-mobile mr-1 align-middle"></span> iOS / Android
        </span>
        <span class="bg-blue-900/40 text-blue-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-mono border border-blue-800/50">
          <span class="i-carbon-stem-leaf-plot mr-1 align-middle"></span> Research
        </span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold m-0 text-white leading-tight mb-6">
        Designing a culturally sensitive mental wellbeing digital solution.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 m-0 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        Bridging the gap between academic stress and help-seeking behavior for international students through <span
          class="text-emerald-400">Participatory Design</span
        > and <span class="text-purple-400">Generative AI</span>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="relative mb-20">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-500/5 blur-3xl rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>

      <div
        class="relative grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-y-8 gap-x-4 p-8 bg-zinc-900/40 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-md shadow-xl"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 md:border-r border-zinc-800/50 pr-4">
          <h3 class="text-[10px] font-bold text-emerald-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-1">My Role</h3>
          <p class="text-white font-medium m-0 leading-tight">Lead UX Researcher & Product Designer</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 md:border-r border-zinc-800/50 md:pl-4 pr-4">
          <h3 class="text-[10px] font-bold text-purple-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-1">Timeline</h3>
          <p class="text-white font-medium m-0 leading-tight">Aug 2024 - Present</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 md:border-r border-zinc-800/50 md:pl-4 pr-4">
          <h3 class="text-[10px] font-bold text-blue-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-1">Tools</h3>
          <p class="text-white font-medium m-0 leading-tight">Figma, React Native, Python</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 md:pl-4">
          <h3 class="text-[10px] font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-1">Team</h3>
          <p class="text-white font-medium m-0 leading-tight">Advisor: Dr. Charlotte Tang</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>

  <section class="mb-16">
    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-6 text-center">Project Roadmap</h3>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 relative">
      <div
        class="hidden md:block absolute top-1/2 left-1/4 right-1/4 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500/50 via-zinc-700 to-purple-500/50 -translate-y-1/2 z-0"
      >
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10 p-6 bg-zinc-900/80 border border-emerald-500/30 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-md shadow-lg">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <span
            class="flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 text-xs font-bold border border-emerald-500/50"
            >1</span
          >
          <span class="text-emerald-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Completed</span>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-2">Academic Research</h4>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm m-0">
          Surveyed 148 international students, performed thematic analysis, and published findings at IEEE FIE 2025.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10 p-6 bg-zinc-900/80 border border-purple-500/30 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-md shadow-lg">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <span
            class="flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-400 text-xs font-bold border border-purple-500/50"
            >2</span
          >
          <span class="text-purple-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-purple-500 animate-pulse"></span> Ongoing
          </span>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-2">Product Development</h4>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm m-0">
          Leading Participatory Design (PD) sessions to build a culturally sensitive app based on Phase 1 insights.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-24 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 relative group">
      <div
        class="absolute -inset-4 bg-emerald-500/10 blur-3xl rounded-[2rem] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-1000"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="relative bg-zinc-900/50 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 p-2 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:-translate-y-2"
      >
        <img
          src="/presentation.jpeg"
          alt="Alex presenting research at IEEE FIE 2025"
          class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl object-cover"
        />
        <div
          class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4 bg-black/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-3"
        >
          <p class="text-[10px] font-mono text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-widest m-0 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="i-carbon-microphone text-sm"></span> IEEE FIE Conference Presentation 2025, Nashville, USA
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Phase 1: Establishing the Foundation</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Before designing a solution, we needed to understand the true scope of the problem. We conducted a mixed-methods
        study surveying <strong>148 international students</strong> across 46 countries.
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-zinc-900/40 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl">
          <span class="i-carbon-data-base text-2xl text-emerald-500 mt-1"></span>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-sm m-0">Quantitative Data</h4>
            <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm m-0 mt-1">
              Evaluated stress occurrences and demographics using Fisher-Freeman-Halton exact tests.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-zinc-900/40 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl">
          <span class="i-carbon-network-4 text-2xl text-emerald-500 mt-1"></span>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-sm m-0">Qualitative Insights</h4>
            <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm m-0 mt-1">
              Utilized Affinity Diagramming on open-ended responses to identify cultural stigma barriers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-24">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
      <span class="i-carbon-microscope text-2xl text-emerald-400"></span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white m-0">The Research Gap</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-zinc-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          International students are a high-risk group for acculturative stress, yet they are the least likely to use
          university health services due to <strong>cultural stigma</strong> and <strong>privacy concerns</strong>.
        </p>
        <div class="p-6 bg-zinc-900/50 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-emerald-500">
          <p class="italic text-zinc-400 m-0">
            "I feel guilty spending money on therapy when my parents are sacrificing so much for my tuition."
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-2 font-mono">— Participant #04, Graduate Student</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
        <div
          class="p-6 bg-zinc-900/30 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-between group hover:border-emerald-500/50 transition-colors"
        >
          <div>
            <span class="block text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-1">93.8%</span>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Academic Pressure</span>
          </div>
          <span class="i-carbon-education text-4xl text-zinc-700 group-hover:text-emerald-500/50 transition-colors"
          ></span>
        </div>
        <div
          class="p-6 bg-zinc-900/30 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-between group hover:border-emerald-500/50 transition-colors"
        >
          <div>
            <span class="block text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-1">93.2%</span>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Financial Stress</span>
          </div>
          <span class="i-carbon-currency text-4xl text-zinc-700 group-hover:text-emerald-500/50 transition-colors"
          ></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-24">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
      <span class="i-carbon-user-profile text-2xl text-emerald-400"></span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white m-0">The Core Audience Profile</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="p-1 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/20 via-zinc-800/50 to-purple-500/20 rounded-3xl">
      <div class="bg-zinc-950 rounded-[1.4rem] p-8 md:p-12 border border-white/5">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] gap-12 items-center">
          <div
            class="flex flex-col items-center text-center md:items-start md:text-left border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-zinc-800 pb-8 md:pb-0 md:pr-8"
          >
            <div
              class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-zinc-800 border-2 border-emerald-500/50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(16,185,129,0.2)]"
            >
              <span class="i-carbon-education text-4xl text-emerald-400"></span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">The International Scholar</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-widest">Primary Archetype</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed m-0">
              Driven but highly vulnerable to acculturative stress, this user group consistently internalizes their
              struggles. They view seeking professional therapy as a "personal weakness" or a financial burden on their
              families.
            </p>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800">
                <span class="i-carbon-warning-alt text-emerald-500 mb-2 block"></span>
                <h4 class="text-white text-sm font-bold mb-1">Primary Pain Points</h4>
                <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs m-0">
                  Severe academic pressure (93.8%), tuition/financial anxiety (93.2%), and isolation.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800">
                <span class="i-carbon-favorite text-emerald-500 mb-2 block"></span>
                <h4 class="text-white text-sm font-bold mb-1">Current Workarounds</h4>
                <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs m-0">
                  Heavy reliance on self-management, social distraction, and informal peer networks.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-24 relative max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <div class="absolute -top-12 -left-12 w-64 h-64 bg-emerald-500/5 blur-[100px] rounded-full pointer-events-none">
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] gap-12 items-center relative z-10">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="i-carbon-presentation-file text-2xl text-emerald-400"></span>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white m-0">Theoretical Framework</h3>
        </div>

        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-lg leading-relaxed m-0">
          Our digital solution is grounded in <span class="text-emerald-400 font-medium italic"
            >Acculturative Stress Theory</span
          >. This framework allowed us to map both extrinsic stressors (financial, academic) and intrinsic stressors
          directly to actionable UX features.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-2">
          <div class="p-4 bg-zinc-900/40 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="text-[10px] font-bold text-emerald-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Extrinsic</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 m-0">
              Academic pressure, financial concerns, and socio-cultural adjustment.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-zinc-900/40 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="text-[10px] font-bold text-emerald-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Intrinsic</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 m-0">Future uncertainty, visa status, and psychological impact.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative group">
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-emerald-500/10 blur-[40px] rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"
        >
        </div>

        <div
          class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 p-4 shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 group-hover:-translate-y-1 w-full sm:w-[320px]"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none bg-[radial-gradient(#000_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:16px_16px]"
          >
          </div>

          <img
            src="/accul.png"
            alt="Acculturative Stress Theory Mapping"
            class="relative z-10 w-full h-auto object-contain drop-shadow-[0_4px_10px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)]"
          />

          <p class="text-center text-[9px] text-zinc-400 mt-3 uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">
            Acculturative Stress Theory Mapping
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-24">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-2">
      <span class="i-carbon-group text-2xl text-purple-400"></span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white m-0">Phase 2: Participatory Design (Ongoing)</h2>
    </div>

    <p class="text-zinc-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl">
      Transitioning from academic research to product development, I am currently leading co-design sessions under the
      advisement of <strong>Dr. Charlotte Tang</strong>. We are actively designing <em>with</em> diverse student groups,
      rather than just <em>for</em> them, to build our high-fidelity application.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mt-12">
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
        <div class="p-8 bg-zinc-900/40 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl relative overflow-hidden group">
          <div
            class="absolute -top-12 -right-12 w-32 h-32 bg-purple-500/5 blur-3xl rounded-full transition-colors group-hover:bg-purple-500/10"
          >
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">The Pivot: "The Wellness Wallet"</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed m-0">
              During our ongoing sticky-note sessions, a critical UX insight emerged. Participants actively rejected the
              idea of a "Clinical App." Instead, they requested a <strong class="text-white">"Stealth UI"</strong>—an
              interface that looks like a productivity tool, allowing them to track mental health in public without fear
              of cultural judgment.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-6 flex gap-3">
              <span
                class="text-[10px] font-mono text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-widest border border-purple-500/20 px-2 py-1 rounded"
                >Stigma Reduction</span
              >
              <span
                class="text-[10px] font-mono text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-widest border border-purple-500/20 px-2 py-1 rounded"
                >UX Insight</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 relative group">
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-purple-500/10 blur-[80px] rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"
          >
          </div>

          <div
            class="relative bg-zinc-900/50 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 p-2 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:-translate-y-2"
          >
            <img
              src="/pd.jpeg"
              alt="Mental Wellbeing App Participatory Design Session"
              class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl object-cover"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 border border-white/5 rounded-xl pointer-events-none"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="mb-24">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
        <span class="i-carbon-pen text-2xl text-blue-400"></span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white m-0">Iterative Prototyping</h2>
      </div>

      <p class="text-zinc-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl">
        Translating the "Stealth UI" concept into a functional architecture required several iterations. Early
        wireframes focused heavily on hiding mental health assessments behind traditional academic planners, but
        usability tests revealed this felt too deceptive. We pivoted to a "Wellness Wallet" approach framing mental
        health as an asset rather than a deficit.
      </p>

      <div class="relative w-full bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 p-4 md:p-8 overflow-hidden">
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.05] pointer-events-none bg-[radial-gradient(#000_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:24px_24px]"
        >
        </div>

        <div
          class="aspect-[21/9] bg-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl border border-zinc-700/50 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden relative group"
        >
          <img
            src="/prototype.jpg"
            alt="Low-Fidelity Wireframes and Sketches"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 mix-blend-luminosity group-hover:mix-blend-normal group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-500"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-6">
          <div class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-zinc-700">
            <h4 class="text-white text-sm font-bold mb-1">Iteration 1: The Planner</h4>
            <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs leading-relaxed m-0">
              Disguised mood tracking inside a study schedule. Discarded: Too confusing for users to navigate.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-blue-500">
            <h4 class="text-white text-sm font-bold mb-1">Iteration 2: The Wallet (Winner)</h4>
            <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs leading-relaxed m-0">
              Framed emotional check-ins as "deposits" to earn campus dining credits, directly tackling financial
              stress.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-zinc-700">
            <h4 class="text-white text-sm font-bold mb-1">AI Integration Focus</h4>
            <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs leading-relaxed m-0">
              Ensured the AI chat interface felt like standard text messaging to maintain privacy in public campus
              spaces.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-24">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
        <span class="i-carbon-mobile text-2xl text-blue-400"></span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white m-0">The Solution</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_300px] gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">AI Peer Support (Gemini)</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
            Leveraging LLMs to provide low-barrier, conversational support. The AI is finetuned to act as an
            "experienced peer" rather than a doctor, reducing the intimidation factor of seeking help.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-zinc-300 text-sm">
              <span class="i-carbon-checkmark-filled text-blue-500 mt-1"></span>
              Culturally aware responses (e.g., understanding filial piety).
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-zinc-300 text-sm">
              <span class="i-carbon-checkmark-filled text-blue-500 mt-1"></span>
              24/7 availability for late-night anxiety spikes.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div
          class="h-[500px] bg-zinc-900 rounded-3xl border border-zinc-700 shadow-2xl shadow-black flex items-center justify-center"
        >
          <img
            src="/aichat.png"
            alt="Mental Wellbeing App UI Mockups"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[300px_1fr] gap-12 items-center">
        <div
          class="h-[500px] bg-zinc-900 rounded-3xl border border-zinc-700 shadow-2xl shadow-black flex items-center justify-center order-2 md:order-1"
        >
          <img
            src="/rewards.png"
            alt="Mental Wellbeing App UI Mockups"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">The Prestige System</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
            Directly addressing the 93.2% financial stress metric. Students earn "Prestige Points" for mindfulness
            streaks, which can be redeemed for small campus dining credits—turning self-care into a tangible financial
            benefit.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-24">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
        <span class="i-carbon-flow-stream text-2xl text-blue-400"></span>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white m-0">User Flowchart</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto relative group">
        <div
          class="absolute -inset-4 bg-cyan-500/10 blur-3xl rounded-[2rem] pointer-events-none opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-1000"
        >
        </div>

        <div
          class="relative w-full bg-zinc-900/40 border border-zinc-800 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden backdrop-blur-md shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 group-hover:border-cyan-500/30"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute top-6 right-6 z-30 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 flex items-center gap-2 pointer-events-none shadow-xl"
          >
            <span class="i-carbon-zoom-in text-blue-600"></span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-black text-zinc-900 uppercase tracking-widest">Move Mouse to Pan</span>
          </div>

          <div
